  "text": "I'm sorry for having so much trouble with these concepts, but they're very difficult to translate, I'm sure, into our understanding and language. And some uh questions may be rather ridiculous, but uh does this higher self have a physical vehicle or some type of vehicle like our physical vehicle? Does it have a bodily complex? I am Ra. This is correct. The Higher Self is of a certain advancement within a sixth, a density, a going into the seventh. After the seventh has been well entered, the mind, body, spirit complex becomes so a totally a mind, body, spirit, complex totality that it begins to gather spiritual mass and approach the octave density. Thus the looking backwards is finished at that point.",
